snippet.textDisplay:
Ultra Instinct Goku? L A M E
WHERE IS BATTLE DAMAGED GI GOKU?!

WHERE IS KRILLIN WITH HAIR?

WHERE ISBASE VEGETA WITH SCOUTER?

WHERE IS SSJ3 GOKU WITH THE HALO?

WHERE IS NAPPA WITH SCOUTER?

WHERE IS PICCOLO WITH CAPE?

WHERE DBS BLUE HAIR TRUNKS?

(Edit: For those who don't have a sense of humor. This is meant to be a joke.)

In all seriousness, though. Even though I suck at this game, I have tons of fun playing it. And I'm very happy to know that this game is still going strong and being supported with new DLC on the way. For a casual Dragon Ball fan like myself I'm Just happy that this game is doing well. I'm never really one to complain about DLC rosters TBH. At the end of the day more characters means more variety which is more fun.

And all of the characters I wanted to be in the game. Are all part of the base roster so I have been very happy since day one.

My favorite old school characters: Piccolo, Lord Yamcha, and Tien shinhan.

My favorite modern DB characters: Lord Beerus, Hit, Zamasu.

And all of them are in the game, so I couldn't be happier. As for you hardcore Dragon Ball fans and competitive players, You all keep doing you and I hope you all enjoy season 3. 😁
